# Tart VM images and working VMs — huge binary blobs, repo-local so
# they stay off the system volume, never committed. TART_HOME must
# be set to this directory (see tart/README.md) for every tart
# invocation in this repo. Everything under tart/ is excluded
# except the README which documents the layout.
tart/*
!tart/README.md

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Workflow docs
docs/discovery/*.md
